---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Viving Mops — Our Story" description="Learn how Viving Mops rescues AI-generated apps and brings hygiene to hybrid human-AI codebases.">
  <div class="py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
          <span class="gradient-text">Our Story</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          How we became the cleanup crew for the AI generation
        </p>
      </div>

      <section class="mb-16">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-lg">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
            <span class="text-4xl mr-4">🚨</span>
            <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">The Problem We Saw</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            In 2024, we noticed a disturbing trend: teams were shipping "AI-generated" applications that looked great in demos but were complete disasters under the hood. 
            <span class="font-semibold text-indigo-600">No tests, broken deployments, spaghetti code, and zero documentation.</span>
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            These weren't just bad codebases—they were <em>vibe-coded</em> applications. Built entirely on AI prompts, deployed with "good vibes," and maintained with hope and prayer. 
            We knew something had to be done.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-16">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-50 to-purple-50 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
            <span class="text-4xl mr-4">🎯</span>
            <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">Our Mission</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            We bring <span class="font-semibold text-indigo-600">hygiene to hybrid human-AI codebases</span>. 
            Our team of experienced DevOps engineers and developers specializes in rescuing applications that were built with more enthusiasm than engineering knowledge.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            We don't just fix code—we transform chaotic AI outputs into production-ready, maintainable systems that your team can actually work with.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-center mb-12">
          What We Clean Up
        </h2>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg hover-lift">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-3xl mr-3">🔧</span>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Broken Pipelines</h3>
            </div>
            <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-2">
              <li>• CI/CD workflows that "work on my machine"</li>
              <li>• Deployment scripts that fail silently</li>
              <li>• Missing environment configurations</li>
              <li>• Zero rollback strategies</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg hover-lift">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-3xl mr-3">🍝</span>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Spaghetti Code</h3>
            </div>
            <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-2">
              <li>• AI-generated functions with no structure</li>
              <li>• Copy-pasted code blocks everywhere</li>
              <li>• No separation of concerns</li>
              <li>• Inconsistent naming conventions</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg hover-lift">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-3xl mr-3">🧪</span>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Missing Tests</h3>
            </div>
            <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-2">
              <li>• Zero test coverage</li>
              <li>• No integration tests</li>
              <li>• Missing error handling tests</li>
              <li>• No performance benchmarks</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg hover-lift">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-3xl mr-3">📚</span>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Documentation Chaos</h3>
            </div>
            <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-2">
              <li>• README files that say "TODO"</li>
              <li>• No API documentation</li>
              <li>• Missing deployment guides</li>
              <li>• Zero architecture diagrams</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-16">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-lg">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
            <span class="text-4xl mr-4">⚡</span>
            <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">Our Process</h2>
          </div>
          
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="bg-indigo-100 rounded-full w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                <span class="text-2xl">🔍</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">1. Assessment</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">We analyze your codebase to identify the chaos and create a cleanup plan.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="bg-indigo-100 rounded-full w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                <span class="text-2xl">🧹</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">2. Cleanup</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">We refactor, test, and document everything to production standards.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="bg-indigo-100 rounded-full w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                <span class="text-2xl">🚀</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">3. Deploy</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">We set up proper CI/CD and hand you a maintainable codebase.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-16">
        <div class="text-center">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
            Meet the Cleanup Crew
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            We're a team of battle-tested DevOps engineers, full-stack developers, and AI skeptics who believe in clean code and proper engineering practices.
          </p>
          
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl mb-4">👨‍💻</div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">DevOps Engineers</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Pipeline whisperers who make CI/CD actually work</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl mb-4">👩‍💻</div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Full-Stack Developers</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Code surgeons who refactor chaos into clarity</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🧪</div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">QA Specialists</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Test architects who ensure nothing breaks</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="text-center">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-600 to-purple-600 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 text-white">
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-6">
            We Bring Hygiene to Hybrid Human-AI Codebases
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl mb-8 opacity-90">
            Ready to transform your vibe-coded chaos into production-ready excellence?
          </p>
          <a 
            href="/viving_mops/contact" 
            class="bg-white hover:bg-gray-100 text-indigo-600 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold transition-all duration-300 hover-lift shadow-lg inline-block"
          >
            Start Your Cleanup Journey 🧹
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
